Package: BalanceMate
Title: Managing, Preprocessing, and Processing Postural Data
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jean", family = "Monéger", email = "moneger.jean@outlook.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1178-1896"))
Description: Facilitates management, preprocessing, and analysis of postural data (e.g., merging data files, time-stamping, creating epochs; applying filters; computing center of pressure and sway path length) for text (.txt) exports from the AMTI NetForce software. Supported by the Vision Action Cognition laboratory at Université Paris Cité.
